title: Modern Chemistry Florida edition 2009
description:
This PDF contains the full textbook of Modern Chemistry from Holt McDougal Florida edition and was copyrighted 2009. This version is still very popular in many high schools among the US. The PDF book is superior to the online counterpart offered by McDougal because:
 * You can select, copy, and paste text from the book
 * Compatible with screen readers
 * You can print out a range of pages
 * It isn't a low-res image like the one on the site
 * You can read it without Flash player
 * You can read it on mobile devices

The book was specially edited to include PDF bookmarks for easy reference to any section or chapter within the book. Also there was careful checking to make sure that each page in the book would match up with it's physical counterpart. So homework assignments given with page numbers should match up exactly.
